title: Publications of the Norwegian-American Historical Association: Travel and Description Series
additional-note: The earliest active renewal for this monographic series, for 'Frontier Parsonage', was filed under Books, rather than under Periodicals.  The CCE renewal record does not specifically mention this series.  Before concluding a volume in the series is in the public domain, search for renewals for it under its distinctive title. We have not systematically checked volume titles for this serial past the fourth volume.
